parameters.name: thd_efs_dot0_gse
parameters.description: EFS_DOT0 (spin-fit, using E dot B=0) electric field vector in GSE coordinates

parameters.name: thd_efs_dot0_gsm
parameters.description: EFS_DOT0 (spin-fit, using E dot B=0) electric field vector in GSM coordinates

parameters.name: thd_efs_dot0_dsl
parameters.description: EFS_DOT0 (spin-fit, using E dot B=0) electric field vector in XYZ despun spacecraft coordinates (DSL)

parameters.name: thd_efs_q_mag
parameters.description: EFS_Q_MAG (Data Quality Parameter: set to NaN for EFS, as there is no good measure of data quality.)

parameters.name: thd_efs_q_pha
parameters.description: EFS_Q_PHA (Data Quality Parameter: Set to NaN, as there is no ggod way to measure data quality for EFS data.)

parameters.name: thd_eff_dot0_gse
parameters.description: EFF_DOT0 (fast-survey, 1/8 sec time resolution, using E dot B=0) electric field vector in GSE coordinates

parameters.name: thd_eff_dot0_gsm
parameters.description: EFF_DOT0 (fast-survey, 1/8 sec time resolution, using E dot B=0) electric field vector in GSM coordinates

parameters.name: thd_eff_dot0_dsl
parameters.description: EFF_DOT0 (fast-survey, 1/8 sec time resolution, , using E dot B=0) electric field vector in XYZ despun spacecraft coordinates (DSL)

parameters.name: thd_eff_q_mag
parameters.description: EFF_Q_MAG (Data Quality Parameter: equal to the spin-fit E34 electric field magnitude divided by the spin-fit E12 electric field magnitude. Good values are near 1.0)

parameters.name: thd_eff_q_pha
parameters.description: EFF_Q_PHA (Data Quality Parameter: equal to the cosine of the angle between the spin-fit E34 electric field and the spin-fit E12 electric field. Good values are near 1.0)

parameters.name: thd_eff_e12_efs
parameters.description: E12_EFS, Ground Spin-fit (using E12), spin plane electric field vector in XYZ despun spacecraft coordinates (DSL)

parameters.name: thd_eff_e34_efs
parameters.description: E34_EFS, Ground Spin-fit (using E34), spin plane electric field vector in XYZ despun spacecraft coordinates (DSL)
